            <description><![CDATA[【不要困了就睡！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%84%91%E9%83%A8%E7%BC%BA%E8%A1%80%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E6%98%A5%E5%9B%B0%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%84%91%E9%83%A8%E7%BC%BA%E8%A1%80%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E6%98%A5%E5%9B%B0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#脑部缺血容易造成春困#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哈欠]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_dahaqi-b1824d3d83.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E6%98%A5%E5%9B%B0%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E6%98%A5%E5%9B%B0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#哪些原因可能导致春困#</span></a> 一到春天就犯困，怎么睡都睡不醒，工作和学习也提不起精神。”春困“是怎么造成的？每天多睡一会能解决吗？季节交替，春天人体气血游走到体表，脑部缺血容易造成春困。专家提示，要劳逸结合解决“春困”，科学用脑，不要困了就睡，建议十点睡六点起，保持良好作息。适量喝茶，注意饮食调理。 <a href="http://t.cn/A6C4TuCm" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
